text: Niyazgulovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Abzanovsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 119 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 60 km from Isyangulovo, 5 km from Abzanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Niyazgulovo, Zianchurinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
